# wcd/1

h1 What the Web Could Have Been
p A proof of concept: documents and applications as separate, honest things.

h2 The Idea
p This page is a static document. It carries no code.
p The renderer drawing it is a WASM bundle, the same kind that runs apps.
p Nothing in this file can execute. It is pure data, inspectable by reading it.

h2 What This Demonstrates
- Documents render with zero runtime of their own
- The renderer is userland, not baked into the engine
- Links move between documents

